[外:BBDA644D17EFD3C020635EE3D90968A5]ああっ・[外:38566B372F4C5A1AEAD4EFA20DECD079]

85
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,669
[外:BBDA644D17EFD3C020635EE3D90968A5]あっ 痛っ…[外:38566B372F4C5A1AEAD4EFA20DECD079]
[外:BBDA644D17EFD3C020635EE3D90968A5]つまりはね・

86
00:08:55,669 --> 00:08:58,772
